"i cant say its a good game. well, to be fair, not a good soccer game. i played fm since it was still called cm (cm3). i had a good memory with the series, but this game seems to be ridiculous. the first thing is the injury. my amc, 2 mcs and 1 winger in the first broken their legs/ribs during my first season. my striker was injured frequently. i never see a real team has a such bad condition. second, the defending system is poor. i can not stop ai scoring, sometimes just from no reasons. they can shoot from 30 yards and scored. they can easily score after 45 mins, no matter i asked my team to be focused or i praised them and asked them to keep up. i set a counter mind, they scored. i played defensive games, they scored. i contained my lads in the box, they still scored. i lost countless games when i was leading by 2 or more goals (like i said, i cant stop ai scoring). the only comfort is that sometimes, i can score a lot either. but having games like 4-4, 5-6, 4-3 every 2 or 3 weeks is not normal at all. i dont use big clubs, but it never troubled me in previous versions. now the game is not fun to me anymore since i dont want to start in a big club. perhaps using a rich club and buy expensive players will solve the problem? i can see that they put a lot of attention in setting the so called interaction part. i have to take interviews in order to get a job. more players wanted to talk to me for personal issues. these are fun. but there were still some bugs. some players wanted to talk to me to ask for a leave. fine, i asked them to stay. but they insisted to leave. ok, i clicked their names to double check the coach report to make sure whether i still need the player. great, i wanted him to stay, so i clicked back in order to continue the conversation. wait... what do you mean i have spoken to the player? several days later , other players will blame me because i treated the one talked to me badly. what the heck? seriously? remember, the most important aspect of fm is the soccer simulation. you will continue losing players like me if you still maintain such a terrible match system.",50.8
